trans-unit.source: Converts WSDL-based policies in a <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.OneWayBindingElement"></xref> into descriptions of the binding elements that can implement these policies for the service.
trans-unit.target: Konverterer WSDL-baserte policyer i en <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.OneWayBindingElement"> </xref> til beskrivelser av de binding som kan implementere disse policyene for tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.OneWayBindingElementImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.OneWayBindingElementImporter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Defines a method that can import custom policy assertions and add implementing binding elements.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en metode som kan importere egendefinerte policydeklarasjon og legge til elementer for implementering binding.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext"></xref> that contains both the policy assertions that can be imported and the collections of binding elements to which implementing binding elements can be added.
